<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>lead someone a dance • lead the dance</xh5><p> <i>lead someone a dance—</i>cause a person much exertion or trouble with no adequate result: The prettiest of all the girls was the schoolie, and didn’t she <u>lead the lads a dance</u>.</p><p> <i>lead the dance—</i>take the lead in a course of action: There is still a very subtle struggle for control. Who will <u>lead the dance</u> and who will follow?</p> </entry>
